    "name": "Lost Tribe",
    "steam_appid": 3028870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aim and throw your spear </strong> to overcome obstacles and defeat enemies. Use it to create platforms that give you a boost to reach new areas. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/43512f313422b3fe11063183af3ce378.poster.avif?t=1768772653\" width=524 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/43512f313422b3fe11063183af3ce378.webm?t=1768772653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/43512f313422b3fe11063183af3ce378.mp4?t=1768772653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Master the winds</strong> with the gliding spear, riding air streams to explore even higher heights. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/d87acb972dea2f32a1f8c39a1e4c585f.poster.avif?t=1768772653\" width=524 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/d87acb972dea2f32a1f8c39a1e4c585f.webm?t=1768772653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/d87acb972dea2f32a1f8c39a1e4c585f.mp4?t=1768772653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a vast world</strong> filled with mysterious encounters and hidden secrets. Use the environment to your advantage by swinging on liana ropes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/667624b5d56bcf21b447d05b4f68f4d1.poster.avif?t=1768772653\" width=524 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/667624b5d56bcf21b447d05b4f68f4d1.webm?t=1768772653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/667624b5d56bcf21b447d05b4f68f4d1.mp4?t=1768772653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pogo off spikes,</strong> throw enemies into them, and discover new areas as you overcome every challenge in your path to save the Tribe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/59b07322354c0e53e4168a9c2af3b2de.poster.avif?t=1768772653\" width=524 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/59b07322354c0e53e4168a9c2af3b2de.webm?t=1768772653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/59b07322354c0e53e4168a9c2af3b2de.mp4?t=1768772653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Venture through a handcrafted 2D pixel art world,</strong> uncovering secrets and gaining new abilities. Face off against corrupted creatures and powerful bosses, each requiring unique skills and strategies to defeat. Use your tribe's ancient wisdom to find them and restore peace to the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/014929d52915113e4ee2ff6ee5f4fd23.poster.avif?t=1768772653\" width=524 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/014929d52915113e4ee2ff6ee5f4fd23.webm?t=1768772653\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028870/extras/014929d52915113e4ee2ff6ee5f4fd23.mp4?t=1768772653\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
